Pong Game Plan

Classes:

Scoreboard
    -display score on the top of the screen
    -score displays on the players side


player piece
    - move the pong player piece with the arrow keys

moving pong
    -move the pong randomly against the screen

detect collision
    -detect when pong collides with player or the wall

detect score
    -detect when pong makes a score
    -reset the pong when score is made